572
00:27:40,759 --> 00:27:41,720
Here's another message.

573
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:43,200
"If you send me 520,"

574
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:44,240
"I wouldn't mind."

575
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,880
What does 520 mean?

576
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:48,079
Think about it.

577
00:27:48,559 --> 00:27:50,680
Aren't they too intimate?

578
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:52,519
Don't listen to his provocation.

579
00:27:52,519 --> 00:27:54,880
They spliced it together like this.

580
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:56,440
I... I never said such things.

581
00:27:56,440 --> 00:27:58,720
They spliced it to frame me!

582
00:27:59,039 --> 00:28:01,240
Tu Huaiwei receiving money
from Jie Yangyang

583
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:04,400
has no bearing on
whether my client incited murder.

584
00:28:05,079 --> 00:28:07,119
I request to present
the next set of evidence.

585
00:28:08,440 --> 00:28:11,599
At that time,
Yang Huihui was steering the boat.

586
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:13,119
She constantly rocked the boat.

587
00:28:13,119 --> 00:28:15,359
I tried to stop her
because the two kids were scared.

588
00:28:15,359 --> 00:28:16,000
She ignored me.

589
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,160
She kept rocking it.

590
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:18,759
I reached out to stop her,

591
00:28:18,759 --> 00:28:19,519
but it made

592
00:28:19,519 --> 00:28:21,000
the boat shake more.

593
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:23,200
When I turned back,
the two kids had already fallen in.

594
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:26,400
You mean, Yang Huihui rocked the boat

595
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:27,839
to make the kids fall in on purpose?

596
00:28:28,799 --> 00:28:30,759
This was Tu Huaiwei's first statement.

597
00:28:31,039 --> 00:28:32,799
He deliberately suggested

598
00:28:32,799 --> 00:28:35,200
that it was Yang Huihui's rocking

599
00:28:35,200 --> 00:28:36,880
that caused the incident.

600
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:37,880
Thereby

601
00:28:38,119 --> 00:28:39,799
he tried to mislead the investigation

602
00:28:39,799 --> 00:28:41,480
onto Yang Huihui.

603
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,319
Defendant Yang Xiaoying.

604
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,799
Yang Huihui is just a child.

605
00:28:46,160 --> 00:28:48,440
Bearing such a terrible accusation

606
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:50,640
would ruin her life.

607
00:28:51,359 --> 00:28:52,680
This is malicious editing!

608
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:54,079
I didn't say that!

609
00:28:54,079 --> 00:28:55,640
It's really malicious editing!

610
00:28:58,039 --> 00:28:59,000
Chief Judge,

611
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:01,880
I request
witness Chen Bixian to testify.

612
00:29:27,359 --> 00:29:28,720
Witness Chen Bixian.

613
00:29:29,119 --> 00:29:31,279
What is your relationship
with Defendant Tu Huaiwei?

614
00:29:32,039 --> 00:29:33,079
I am

615
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:35,200
Tu Huaiwei's mother.

616
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,272
He...

617
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:41,519
Didn't you tell me
your parents were died?

618
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:47,599
Defendant, pay attention to court order.

619
00:29:48,279 --> 00:29:48,880
Chen Bixian.

620
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,279
Please tell us what you know

621
00:29:50,279 --> 00:29:52,000
related to this case.

622
00:29:54,279 --> 00:29:55,319
Yang Xiaoying

623
00:29:56,279 --> 00:29:58,720
and her daughter have terrible tempers.

624
00:29:58,720 --> 00:30:03,240
Xiaohua and Xiaohu often got beaten,

625
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:06,440
very severely.

626
00:30:09,519 --> 00:30:10,279
Let me play.

627
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:11,640
Give it to me.

628
00:30:12,079 --> 00:30:13,519
Let go! Give it!

629
00:30:13,519 --> 00:30:14,519
- No.
- Give it to me!

630
00:30:14,519 --> 00:30:15,359
- No!
- No!

631
00:30:15,359 --> 00:30:16,200
Give me!

632
00:30:16,319 --> 00:30:17,240
No!

633
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:18,480
- No.
- Give it to me!

634
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,519
No!

635
00:30:19,519 --> 00:30:21,200
Mom, they're bullying me again!

636
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,119
Give it to me!

637
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:26,480
Huihui, move.

638
00:30:31,279 --> 00:30:32,119
Stop it!

639
00:30:32,119 --> 00:30:33,000
Give it or not?

640
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:35,400
Give it or not!

641
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:43,440
What did I tell you?

642
00:30:43,839 --> 00:30:44,920
Why are you so meddlesome?

643
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:46,039
Why annoyed her?

644
00:30:46,039 --> 00:30:47,000
Why so meddlesome?

645
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:53,039
Are you being nice?

646
00:30:53,039 --> 00:30:54,000
Dare run?

647
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:57,440
Stop!

648
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:58,759
Pretending here?

649
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:00,519
Xiaohu

650
00:31:00,680 --> 00:31:01,599
even got

651
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,880
his bone broken.

652
00:31:04,759 --> 00:31:06,599
Who did that?

653
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,200
Should I tell the truth?

654
00:31:10,839 --> 00:31:11,519
Yes.

655
00:31:16,759 --> 00:31:17,559
It was

656
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:22,119
Tu Huaiwei.

657
00:31:22,119 --> 00:31:24,960
Mom, don't help them.

658
00:31:25,519 --> 00:31:26,759
Witness Chen Bixian.

659
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:28,920
When you saw the children being abused,

660
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,519
why didn't you call the police?

661
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:34,119
I... I thought,

662
00:31:34,599 --> 00:31:37,519
my son isn't a bad person.

663
00:31:37,759 --> 00:31:40,519
I talked to him in private

664
00:31:40,519 --> 00:31:42,519
not to treat the kids that way.

665
00:31:42,519 --> 00:31:44,920
He told me
he was just acting out of anger.

666
00:31:45,079 --> 00:31:49,279
He promised that Xiaohua and Xiaohu

667
00:31:49,279 --> 00:31:50,519
would live a good life.

668
00:31:50,519 --> 00:31:52,079
What did he mean by "a good life"?

669
00:31:52,240 --> 00:31:53,839
Housing compensation.

670
00:31:54,799 --> 00:31:57,319
My house is being demolished.

671
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:58,599
That's my house!

672
00:31:58,599 --> 00:32:00,039
You're coveting my house?

673
00:32:00,039 --> 00:32:01,119
Shameless!

674
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:04,240
Your whole family is nothing
but a bunch of thieves.

675
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:05,640
You deserve

676
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:06,480
to be wiped out!

677
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:07,240
Objection.

678
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:08,400
The witness's statements

679
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:09,839
are irrelevant to the case.

680
00:32:09,839 --> 00:32:10,599
Shut up!

681
00:32:10,599 --> 00:32:12,039
I paid for your expenses too!

682
00:32:12,599 --> 00:32:13,599
Tu Huaiwei.

683
00:32:14,279 --> 00:32:15,599
Now I finally understand

684
00:32:15,799 --> 00:32:17,799
why you tried to frame Huihui.

685
00:32:18,240 --> 00:32:19,319
You just wanted both of us

686
00:32:19,319 --> 00:32:20,160
to get into trouble,

687
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:21,839
so that you could take over my house!

688
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:22,920
Tu Huaiwei!

689
00:32:23,079 --> 00:32:24,480
What did you say the night before?

690
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:26,200
What did you say to me?

691
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:26,960
Chief Judge,

692
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,640
my client is emotionally unstable.

693
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:30,119
I am perfectly stable!

694
00:32:30,119 --> 00:32:31,079
Tu Huaiwei.

695
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,480
You said I was your family,

696
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:33,519
your only family,

697
00:32:33,519 --> 00:32:35,279
the closest person to you.

698
00:32:35,279 --> 00:32:36,119
Is this how

699
00:32:36,119 --> 00:32:37,799
you treat your closest family?

700
00:32:38,319 --> 00:32:39,079
Objection.

701
00:32:41,079 --> 00:32:42,039
He said...

702
00:32:42,039 --> 00:32:42,920
He said

703
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,400
there were no cameras out there.

704
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:46,720
The kids would die
without anyone knowing.

705
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:09,039
Let's go down together.

706
00:33:11,279 --> 00:33:12,559
Defendant Tu Huaiwei.

707
00:33:12,559 --> 00:33:13,799
Do you admit

708
00:33:13,920 --> 00:33:16,880
to conspiring
with Defendant Yang Xiaoying?

709
00:33:20,279 --> 00:33:20,839
I do not.

710
00:33:20,839 --> 00:33:22,039
I've been framed.

711
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:24,160
Son,

712
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:26,359
we cannot

713
00:33:27,799 --> 00:33:30,279
live like parasites anymore.

714
00:33:30,279 --> 00:33:32,759
We need to live like human beings.

715
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,079
It's all my fault

716
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,279
for not educating you well.

717
00:33:38,279 --> 00:33:40,559
It is all my fault.

718
00:33:42,319 --> 00:33:43,240
Judge,

719
00:33:43,759 --> 00:33:46,079
can I take the blame for him?

720
00:33:46,079 --> 00:33:48,799
I'll take it, okay?

721
00:33:48,799 --> 00:33:49,720
Judge.

722
00:33:50,319 --> 00:33:52,279
Can you stop pretending?

723
00:33:52,279 --> 00:33:53,599
What are you doing?

724
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:55,920
You are pushing me to my death!

725
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:57,599
What good does it do you if I die?

726
00:33:58,480 --> 00:34:00,440
Even a tiger doesn't eat its cubs.

727
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:06,759
I can't believe that's from your mouth.

728
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:09,760
Tu Huaiwei.

729
00:34:10,239 --> 00:34:11,079
You

730
00:34:12,199 --> 00:34:13,599
took Xiaohua

731
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:15,719
and Xiaohu

732
00:34:16,679 --> 00:34:18,119
for a boat ride.

733
00:34:18,239 --> 00:34:23,400
Do you know how happy they were?

734
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:28,320
A tiger doesn't abandon its cubs?

735
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:32,000
Then how could you hurt Xiaohu?

736
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:36,840
Thinking of this makes me hate you.

737
00:34:37,679 --> 00:34:40,800
How could you be so cruel?

738
00:34:59,028 --> 00:35:00,920
(Out of the maze)

739
00:35:00,920 --> 00:35:02,000
Why are you looking for us?

740
00:35:03,400 --> 00:35:04,360
I plead guilty.

741
00:35:04,719 --> 00:35:05,480
Yang Xiaoying,

742
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:07,639
you are an instigator
of intentional homicide.

743
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,840
Your actions are as vicious
as Tu Huaiwei's.

744
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:10,719
Are you clear?

745
00:35:13,559 --> 00:35:15,000
Even you plead guilty now,

746
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:16,760
it won't affect your sentencing.

747
00:35:17,159 --> 00:35:21,312
Will having a letter of forgiveness
save me from death?

748
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:22,119
What?

749
00:35:22,119 --> 00:35:23,200
A letter of forgiveness.

750
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:24,960
I'll pay the money.

751
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:27,440
I'm willing to pay.

752
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:27,960
800,000.

753
00:35:27,960 --> 00:35:29,639
I have a house. I can pay.

754
00:35:30,199 --> 00:35:30,960
Is it okay?

755
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:33,079
Xiaohua will need a lot of money
on medical treatment.

756
00:35:33,079 --> 00:35:34,159
They have no money.

757
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:36,119
I'm willing to pay for that.

758
00:35:36,639 --> 00:35:37,840
I have a house, I can do it.

759
00:35:37,840 --> 00:35:39,119
Even a million.

760
00:35:42,199 --> 00:35:43,199
Only if it can save me.

761
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:44,119
You regret it now?

762
00:35:44,119 --> 00:35:45,480
What were you doing back then?

763
00:35:45,639 --> 00:35:47,400
I also have a daughter.

764
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:49,079
You realize you have a daughter now.

765
00:35:58,291 --> 00:36:03,072
(To Sister Huihui)

766
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,800
As a Prosecutor,

767
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:08,880
I know

768
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:11,840
I should be calm and rational.

769
00:36:12,199 --> 00:36:13,519
But at this moment,

770
00:36:14,519 --> 00:36:16,239
I am furious.

771
00:36:16,599 --> 00:36:18,079
A child aged five or six

772
00:36:18,639 --> 00:36:21,400
should be running around outside,

773
00:36:21,599 --> 00:36:22,920
laughing loud,

774
00:36:24,199 --> 00:36:26,320
and be loved and cherished.

775
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:28,320
But at such a young age,

776
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:31,320
Xiaohu has left this world forever.

777
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,480
His sister

778
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:35,719
will carry the trauma of her injuries,

779
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:37,559
and the shadow

780
00:36:37,559 --> 00:36:39,559
of her own biological father
wanted to kill her,

781
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:42,639
for the rest of her life.

782
00:36:43,599 --> 00:36:45,239
I don't know how this girl

783
00:36:45,239 --> 00:36:46,719
will face

784
00:36:46,719 --> 00:36:48,480
her future life.

785
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:51,599
Even a fierce tiger won't eat its cubs.

786
00:36:52,079 --> 00:36:54,480
But he used such cruel means

787
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:56,480
to kill his own kid.

788
00:36:57,480 --> 00:36:59,159
This is a complete loss of humanity,

789
00:36:59,159 --> 00:37:01,960
utterly heartless.

790
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,519
Tu Huaiwei and Yang Xiaoying

791
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:06,320
regarded Tu Huaiwei's
biological children

792
00:37:06,440 --> 00:37:07,800
as obstacles to their marriage.

793
00:37:08,119 --> 00:37:09,159
They conspired together

794
00:37:09,159 --> 00:37:11,639
to murder the children
by faking an accidental drowning,

795
00:37:11,639 --> 00:37:13,320
resulting in one child's death

796
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:16,039
and the other's severe injury.

797
00:37:16,239 --> 00:37:18,159
Their actions severely violated the law,

798
00:37:18,159 --> 00:37:19,840
disregarded human morals,

799
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,480
and trampled on societal conscience.

800
00:37:21,719 --> 00:37:23,760
Their motive was despicable,

801
00:37:24,119 --> 00:37:25,840
their conduct particularly vile,

802
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:27,599
their methods heinous,

803
00:37:27,719 --> 00:37:29,800
the consequences extremely serious,

804
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:32,039
and the social impact extremely adverse.

805
00:37:32,039 --> 00:37:34,239
They should be severely punished
according to the law.

806
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:36,639
Defendants Tu Huaiwei and Yang Xiaoying

807
00:37:36,639 --> 00:37:38,559
violated Articles 232 and 260

808
00:37:38,559 --> 00:37:39,920
of the Criminal Law

809
00:37:40,079 --> 00:37:41,559
of the People's Republic of China,

810
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:44,800
constituting intentional homicide
and abuse.

811
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:48,199
According to Article 29 the Criminal Law
of the People's Republic of China,

812
00:37:48,199 --> 00:37:49,280
multiple crimes applies.

813
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:52,880
We suggest to sentence
Tu Huaiwei and Yang Xiaoying

814
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:54,480
to death penalty.

815
00:37:59,712 --> 00:38:01,280
The court pronounces the judgment.

816
00:38:01,408 --> 00:38:02,656
(Supervised by
the Supreme People's Court)

817
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:04,400
All rise.

818
00:38:13,039 --> 00:38:15,159
According to Articles 232,

819
00:38:15,159 --> 00:38:16,760
Article 260 and Article 29

820
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:18,360
of the Criminal Law

821
00:38:18,519 --> 00:38:19,920
of the People's Republic of China,

822
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:21,159
the judgment is as follows.

823
00:38:21,519 --> 00:38:22,239
One.

824
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:25,320
Defendant Tu Huaiwei,
for the crime of intentional homicide,

825
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:26,519
is sentenced to death penalty,

826
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:29,320
and for the crime of child abuse,

827
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:31,119
sentenced to two years in prison.

828
00:38:31,119 --> 00:38:32,320
Combined punishment,

829
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:34,599
Tu Huaiwei is sentenced to death.

830
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:35,800
Two.

831
00:38:36,039 --> 00:38:37,360
Defendant Yang Xiaoying,

832
00:38:37,472 --> 00:38:39,039
for the crime of intentional homicide,

833
00:38:39,039 --> 00:38:40,280
is sentenced to death penalty.

834
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:41,639
Defendant Yang Xiaoying,

835
00:38:41,639 --> 00:38:42,679
for the crime of abuse,

836
00:38:42,679 --> 00:38:44,719
is sentenced to two years in prison.

837
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:46,079
Combined punishment,

838
00:38:46,079 --> 00:38:47,960
Yang Xiaoying is sentenced
to death penalty.

839
00:39:52,679 --> 00:39:54,440
Is it necessary to come here?

840
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:56,199
We're all quite busy.

841
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:58,079
You're not the sentimental type.

842
00:39:58,336 --> 00:39:59,159
It's been years.

843
00:39:59,159 --> 00:40:00,559
Still can't get past this?

844
00:40:00,679 --> 00:40:01,400
Come on.

845
00:40:03,039 --> 00:40:04,280
I can.

846
00:40:08,599 --> 00:40:10,360
They've renovated this place.

847
00:40:11,559 --> 00:40:12,599
Look, the decoration.

848
00:40:15,960 --> 00:40:18,199
There's even
a legal education room here.

849
00:40:18,707 --> 00:40:22,912
(Legal Education Room)

850
00:40:23,199 --> 00:40:23,880
Look.

851
00:40:24,519 --> 00:40:26,119
Now there are desks and chairs.

852
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:31,159
When we first met,

853
00:40:31,159 --> 00:40:32,960
you were barely

854
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:35,360
taller than this podium, right?

