922
00:43:10,360 --> 00:43:11,960
for child abuse cases.

923
00:43:12,159 --> 00:43:13,800
This system requires

924
00:43:13,800 --> 00:43:15,679
that state agencies, organizations

925
00:43:15,679 --> 00:43:18,440
and officials authorized

926
00:43:18,440 --> 00:43:20,360
to exercise public power by law,

927
00:43:20,360 --> 00:43:22,679
and personnel working in sectors

928
00:43:22,679 --> 00:43:24,960
that frequently interact with minors,

929
00:43:25,079 --> 00:43:25,960
If they found

930
00:43:25,960 --> 00:43:27,639
or even suspect,

931
00:43:27,639 --> 00:43:30,159
that a minor has been harmed

932
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:32,480
or is at risk of unlawful harm,

933
00:43:32,599 --> 00:43:34,960
they must immediately
report to the police

934
00:43:34,960 --> 00:43:36,000
or authorities.

935
00:43:47,039 --> 00:43:48,039
Let me

936
00:43:49,239 --> 00:43:50,119
tell you

937
00:43:50,119 --> 00:43:50,960
about

938
00:43:51,800 --> 00:43:53,360
a case I handled recently.

939
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:54,960
There are two children

940
00:43:55,280 --> 00:43:56,159
