944
00:44:01,320 --> 00:44:03,320
(remarried.)

945
00:44:03,639 --> 00:44:06,039
(From that point on,)

946
00:44:06,360 --> 00:44:08,960
(the twins never had a good day.)

947
00:44:09,400 --> 00:44:10,599
(Living under another's roof,)

948
00:44:10,960 --> 00:44:12,039
(being beaten and scolded,)

949
