tried to kill them.

959
00:44:33,239 --> 00:44:34,559
You might ask,

960
00:44:35,199 --> 00:44:36,480
when such things happened

961
00:44:36,480 --> 00:44:38,000
and the children suffered,

962
00:44:38,199 --> 00:44:39,719
