Didn't anyone try to stop it?

964
00:44:42,639 --> 00:44:43,639
Someone saw that.

965
00:44:44,320 --> 00:44:45,480
The neighbor saw it.

966
00:44:46,199 --> 00:44:47,360
The teacher knew it.

967
00:44:48,440 --> 00:44:49,519
The doctor knew it.

968
00:44:50,239 --> 00:44:52,039
Even pedestrians on the road knew it.

969
00:44:54,960 --> 00:44:56,440
But among so many people,

970
00:44:59,199 --> 00:45:02,599
not a single person stood up to help.

971
00:45:03,679 --> 00:45:04,760
Not even one.

972
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:09,800
Maybe they were

973
00:45:09,800 --> 00:45:11,679
afraid of retaliation

974
00:45:12,400 --> 00:45:13,760
from the parents.

975
00:45:13,960 --> 00:45:15,239
Or they believed

976
00:45:16,639 --> 00:45:17,960
good people don't get rewarded.

977
00:45:18,840 --> 00:45:19,679
Is there any chance

978
00:45:19,679 --> 00:45:21,320
