We never told them

984
00:45:31,360 --> 00:45:32,719
that they could

985
00:45:32,840 --> 00:45:33,960
and should step in

986
00:45:33,960 --> 00:45:34,920
and help,

987
00:45:35,320 --> 00:45:36,840
even if it was a misunderstanding.

988
00:45:40,079 --> 00:45:41,480
Actually, I've been through

989
00:45:44,960 --> 00:45:46,360
