When I was very young,

994
00:45:59,039 --> 00:46:01,400
I truly wished someone could stand up,

995
00:46:01,559 --> 00:46:02,400
speak for me

996
00:46:02,400 --> 00:46:03,199
and help me.

997
00:46:05,519 --> 00:46:06,639
So in this case,

998
00:46:06,639 --> 00:46:08,360
when I meet Xiaohua,

999
00:46:09,840 --> 00:46:11,159
I promised her

1000
00:46:11,840 --> 00:46:12,880
that I'd protect her.

1001
00:46:14,599 --> 00:46:15,880
I want to keep that promise.

1002
00:46:19,960 --> 00:46:20,800
So,

1003
00:46:23,039 --> 00:46:24,320
today,

1004
00:46:25,119 --> 00:46:26,159
I sincerely ask you all

1005
00:46:27,480 --> 00:46:31,159
to join me in helping children
like Xiaohua and Xiaohu,

1006
00:46:32,239 --> 00:46:34,159
